---
layout: null
---
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xsl:stylesheet version="1.0"
  xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform"
  xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"
  xmlns:rss="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/"
  exclude-result-prefixes="atom rss">

<xsl:output method="html" encoding="UTF-8" indent="yes"/>

<xsl:template match="/">
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title><xsl:value-of select="/rss/channel/title"/> - RSS 订阅源</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      color: #404040;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #e8e8e8;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #0085a1;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .header .subtitle {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .rss-notice {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .rss-notice h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #0085a1;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .rss-notice h2::before {
      content: "📡";
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .rss-notice p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .rss-notice .feed-url {
      background: #f0f0f0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      font-family: "SF Mono", "Fira Code", Consolas, monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #0085a1;
      word-break: break-all;
      margin: 12px 0;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .rss-notice .steps {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }
    .rss-notice .steps li {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      padding: 4px 0;
      padding-left: 24px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .rss-notice .steps li::before {
      content: attr(data-step);
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #0085a1;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .post-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .post-item {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .post-item:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,133,161,0.1);
    }
    .post-item .post-title {
      font-size: 17px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .post-item .post-title a {
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .post-item .post-title a:hover {
      color: #0085a1;
    }
    .post-item .post-date {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #999;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .post-item .post-tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .post-item .tag {
      background: #e8f4f7;
      color: #0085a1;
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #aaa;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #0085a1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1><xsl:value-of select="/rss/channel/title"/></h1>
      <div class="subtitle"><xsl:value-of select="/rss/channel/description"/></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rss-notice">
      <h2>这是 RSS 订阅源</h2>
      <p>此页面供 RSS 阅读器使用。你可以将下面的地址复制到你的 RSS 阅读器中，即可自动接收博客更新。</p>
      <div class="feed-url"><xsl:value-of select="/rss/channel/atom:link/@href"/></div>
      <p><strong>什么是 RSS？</strong> RSS 是一种信息订阅方式，就像"订阅报纸"一样——博客有新文章时，阅读器会自动提醒你，不用自己来刷网页。</p>
      <ul class="steps">
        <li data-step="1. ">下载一个 RSS 阅读器（推荐：手机端 FeedMe / Inoreader；电脑端 Fluent Reader / Inoreader 网页版）</li>
        <li data-step="2. ">复制上面的订阅地址</li>
        <li data-step="3. ">在阅读器中添加订阅，粘贴地址</li>
        <li data-step="4. ">完成！新文章会自动推送到你的阅读器</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:20px; color:#0085a1; margin-bottom:16px;">📰 最新文章</h2>
    <ul class="post-list">
      <xsl:for-each select="/rss/channel/item">
        <li class="post-item">
          <div class="post-title">
            <a href="{link}"><xsl:value-of select="title"/></a>
          </div>
          <div class="post-date"><xsl:value-of select="pubDate"/></div>
          <div class="post-tags">
            <xsl:for-each select="category">
              <span class="tag"><xsl:value-of select="."/></span>
            </xsl:for-each>
          </div>
        </li>
      </xsl:for-each>
    </ul>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Powered by <a href="{/rss/channel/link}"><xsl:value-of select="/rss/channel/title"/></a> · Generated by Jekyll</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
</xsl:template>
</xsl:stylesheet>
